      <t>&lt;p&gt;The Real-Time Transport Protocol (RTP) is used to transmit media in telephony and video conferencing applications.  This document describes the guidelines to evaluate new congestion control algorithms for interactive point-to-point real-time media.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
